Looking for a sweet, easy to make dip that will have your friends and family in dessert heaven? We’ve got you covered with this Dunkaroo-inspired dip. Pair it with the crunchy, slightly salty deliciousness of our Pistachio THINaddictives for goodness in every bite!​

Ingredients:​
Funfetti boxed cake mix​
1 container Cool Whip​
1.5 cups Vanilla yogurt​
Sprinkles​

Combine cake mix, whipped topping and yogurt. Top with sprinkles and enjoy!
How many cups is too many? The limit does not exist when you have Nonni’s Cioccolati Biscotti to dunk into every cup!​
